(firstQuint)Dose Finding Study for Combination of Capecitabine, Lapatinib and Vinorelbine in Metastatic Breast Cancer.

 The combination of lapatinib with capecitabine ist a standard therapy fur Her2 positive metastatic breast cancer.

 This study combines this therapy with the additional antimitotic mode of function by vinorelbine.

.

 Dose Finding Study for Combination of Capecitabine, Lapatinib and Vinorelbine in Metastatic Breast Cancer@highlight

The purpose of the study is to investigate safety and efficiency of the triple combination of capecitabine, lapatinib and vinorelbine in patients with metastatic breast cancer.

